headline: E.l.f. Beauty CEO talks 'incredible momentum' since Hailey Bieber deal
summary: Cosmetics company e.l.f. Beauty (ELF) is glowing up Thursday morning after releasing strong fiscal third quarter earnings results while raising its full-year guidance. e.l.f. Beauty Chairman and CEO Tarang Amin speaks with Yahoo Finance Executive Editor Brian Sozzi about the brand's momentum since acquiring Hailey Bieber's skincare line Rhode last year. Amin also comments on the company's product roadmap, its core business growth, and sales inside major retailers like Costco (COST) and Walmart (WMT).
